a href=\"/wiki/Cadmus\" title=\"Cadmus\">Cadmus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Agave\" title=\"Agave\">Agave</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Pentheus\" title=\"Pentheus\">Pentheus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Autonoe\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Autonoe\">Autonoe</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ino_(Greek_mythology)\" title=\"Ino (Greek mythology)\">Ino</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Films</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Bacchantes_(film)\" title=\"The Bacchantes (film)\">The Bacchantes</a></i> (1961)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Dionysus_in_%2769\" title=\"Dionysus in &#39;69\">Dionysus in '69</a></i> (1970)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Bacchae_(film)\" title=\"The Bacchae (film)\">The Bacchae</a></i> (2002)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Plays</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Dionysus_in_69_(play)\" title=\"Dionysus in 69 (play)\">Dionysus in 69</a></i> (1968)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/A_Mouthful_of_Birds\" title=\"A Mouthful of Birds\">A Mouthful of Birds</a></i> (1986)</li>\n<li><i><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">The Lightning Child</a></i> (2013)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Operas</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Bassarids\" title=\"The Bassarids\">The Bassarids</a></i> (1966)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style